{"tid":88891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[串鳩薯片] 梁振英: 若香港休養生息而對手並不如此　可想像後果","createTime":"2017-01-21T03:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T17:22:01.000Z","uid":18074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"11a8fbdc097649cfbc8d04e94662d7b4d2d4fd39","tid":88891,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T03:25:21.000Z","msg":"行政長官梁振英表示，在全球一體化下，各地之間的競爭難免會越來越激烈，若香港休養生息、無為而治，而香港的競爭對手並不如此，相信大家都可以想像到後果。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英在一個電台節目表示，政府的經濟功能及角色要改變，因時制宜，他強調一帶一路是本港經濟發展的新引擎，政府會繼續支持。<br />\n<br />\n被問到不少香港人對內地仍有戒心，梁振英說，最好的方法是多向社會解釋，讓青少年多到內地了解發展情況。他相信，越來越多人接受一個現實，就是香港在多方面的發展都離不開中國內地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1309059-20170121.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1309059-20170121.htm&d=8dA%2FicDEPNKOZgrjHyrZlpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=3c1d8d08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1309059-20170121.htm&h=28bd2126\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1309059-20170121.htm</a>"},{"pid":"462e4fdfcf4ff15fd7714e8b81812df43f9dbfa4","tid":88891,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T03:27:38.000Z","msg":"香港俾你搞完5年，唔覺得有咩進步？除左赤化左好多，多左大陸人搶資源，香港人有咩得益？"},{"pid":"66d9f54b4b94ee7ed618ddfbb2417f89e36caf03","tid":88891,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T03:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a1d6e1321e0721d8c7e1644ec80dc27cd7a037b","tid":88891,"uid":65056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:58:07.000Z","msg":"其實品客既休養生息根本唔係佢果個意思，品客明顯係想話少搞政治，多做實事啦"},{"pid":"dbe6c3affd8f1fdcdb6a7e4550fe0ebfeb485f2d","tid":88891,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T10:26:53.000Z","msg":"算吧啦<br />\n689呢D得把口<br />\n乜7都冇做過"},{"pid":"e8e47d5b4f2a4ff51c76982c9dde5601e